  "title": "Field Engineer (Security Systems) | Company Transport Provided",
  "description": "<p>1. Installation, maintenance and servicing of a wide variety of equipment including but not limited to:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>General security systems</li>\n  <li>Alarm systems</li>\n  <li>CCTV systems</li>\n  <li>Access control systems</li>\n</ul>\n<p>2. Troubleshoot problems encountered on site</p>\n<p>3. Diagnose and resolve issues related to network connectivity, server performance, and communication between security systems (e.g., CCTV, alarm systems, access control systems).</p>\n<p>4. Provide feedback to management on issues faced on the ground</p>\n<p>5. Perform routine maintenance and firmware updates on servers, network devices, and security system software to ensure systems remain reliable and up-to-date</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a NITEC or Diploma in Engineering (Electrical/ Electronic/ Information Technology) or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years’ experience in Operational Technology/ Information Technology industry</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of networking and IP/TCP protocol</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge in CCTV, Access Control and System Server etc.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in security-related tasks such as OS tightening, patching and updating, virus scanning will be an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>IT Certification in windows system &amp; storage, network, database, virtualization, cloud technologies will be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and positive working attitude.</li>\n  <li><strong>Candidate must possess a Class 3 driving licence</strong></li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Annual Wage Supplement (13th month) and Performance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Medical and Dental Benefits</li>\n  <li>Corporate Insurance coverage</li>\n  <li>Annual Pay Increment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Clarice Lim (R1656152) | Anchor Search Group Pte Ltd (17C8528)</p>",
